同月26日，大馬國營電台TV2顯示獎牌數量時再度發生國旗對調的狀況<ref>{{Cite web |url=http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1676514/%E4%B8%9C%E8%BF%90%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%88%E4%B9%8C%E9%BE%99%EF%BC%8Etv2%E6%90%9E%E9%94%998%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%97 |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2017-08-26 |archive-date=2017-08-30 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170830035644/http://www.sinchew.com.my/node/1676514/%E4%B8%9C%E8%BF%90%E4%BC%9A%E5%8F%88%E4%B9%8C%E9%BE%99%EF%BC%8Etv2%E6%90%9E%E9%94%998%E5%9B%BD%E5%9B%BD%E6%97%97 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

